title: Second Mexican Governor in Two Days Tests Positive for Coronavirus
description: A second Mexican governor announced that he tested positive for the novel coronavirus (COVID-19). The announcement comes just one day after another governor who had recent meetings with Mexico’s president also announced his infection with the virus.
